response.about: POOLSE (ART MALEEV) started his creative way back in 2006. That was a DNB music. Slightly he moved to Drum and Bass genre. In early 2006, POOLSE got totally familiar with FL Studio and began his Drum and Bass production. Nu Jump Up, Jump Up - that's what you'd found in POOLSE's tracks. Since recent time POOLSE is artist of promising label "SOM REC " based in St.-Petersburg running by DJ SWOOLADGE. POOLSE tracks are played in Russia and many other countries. You could often hear his tracks on Radio Record (106.3) in "Russian Hour Pirate Station" radioshow. Also he could be heard on many English radioshows (on Charge FM, Crisis FM, Kool FM) Signed on, Deadly records, G-13 Records, DJ/Producer Support: DJ Spice (UK), Dub Zero (UK), Dub Alley (AU), DJ Messy (UK), Propa G (UK), and etc
